Package net.explorviz.security.services.exceptions

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    UserValidationService
    Injectable service that contains utility methods for UserCredentials validation.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DuplicateUserException
    Sub-Exception of UserCrudException that is thrown when a user is tried to persist, that already exists.
    MalformedBatchRequestException
    Denotes that the given UserBatchRequest can not be fulfilled.
    UserCrudException
    Exception for all errors that occur during user CRUD operations.
